content:
Map Outputs to Summary Fields

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on.

To build and manage Work Summaries:

Customize Application
AND
Edit on records OR Modify All Data

From Map Outputs to Record Fields, select Edit.
For the Summary, Issue, and Resolution, select the Case field where you want to map each output.
We recommend mapping summaries to fields with a long text format.

Click Save. Don't change field mappings after setup.

To turn on Work Summaries and show Einstein generative AI outputs to agents in the console, turn on Case Summaries.
title: Mapping Outputs to Summary Fields in Service Cloud
